{"tid":873143,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖][肥G][中非打]百里香食評","createTime":"2018-10-23T08:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T08:47:16.000Z","uid":218091,"like":42,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"86573aef3ea02b075ec304a7e73a676e69df9086","tid":873143,"uid":218091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"今日我同朋友去咗被連登仔瘋狂吹捧嘅百里香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到個熟食市場 第一個感覺就係衛生麻麻 又有陣味<br />\n好多開放式廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環境3/10<br />\n慢慢探下路之後 上到一樓轉咗幾個靚彎 即刻見到百里香個招牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/155228_dbf6910adf6c2ac9ed318899f82dadb8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F155228_dbf6910adf6c2ac9ed318899f82dadb8.png&h=fcceab69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面環境比出面好 偏細 打算搵下邊個係印度仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但搵唔到<br />\n之後我當然拿拿聲拎個餐牌揀下嘢食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/155336_915c18cf70ec9679286ac46c2c1cbf13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F155336_915c18cf70ec9679286ac46c2c1cbf13.png&h=c5a840a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山長水遠嚟到當然要試下佢隻撚手燒雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外再是但叫咗個豬肉薄餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋唔知咩味嘅雞翼小食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/155600_d085729be135d9784f2009cfd7417c06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F155600_d085729be135d9784f2009cfd7417c06.png&h=a03f49f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗌完嘢食 等咗一陣 就上咗一湯一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾快<br />\n個湯我覺得比較淡 但味道幾好 而且真材實料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有菜有紅蘿蔔有蜆肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個包就麻麻地 一嚟太細太薄啦 二嚟都係淡唔夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/141335_96ca38bb879a016db041a39693ca583e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F141335_96ca38bb879a016db041a39693ca583e.png&h=446d22ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲完湯食完包 等咗五分鐘左右就上主菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時間方面唔算耐 可能我比較早去 唔多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主菜方面就有燒雞同豬肉夾餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先講燒雞 賣相就6/10 有色有味嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉質都唔錯7/10 雞胸雞背就眾所鳩知難食 但佢算ok 起碼咬得斷 但都唔係好食 薯皇就無乜特別 夠脆夠熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份量好足 45蚊 12點幾前好似平5蚊 好抵屌 一個男人食應該好撚飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/143918_84fa6c2d0503c132e32b4bba3acf8762.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F143918_84fa6c2d0503c132e32b4bba3acf8762.png&h=612a25ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬肉夾餅方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個人覺得好正 正過燒雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮薄餡靚 個皮脆脆地 D豬肉又比想像中好食 食落無渣 抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  9/10<br />\n但個人嚟講 D紅色嘅醬就麻麻啦<br />\n反而D涼拌菜就幾Fresh幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣相方面就7/10 大家有眼睇啦 幾colorful又有d懶係靚嘅白色醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份量方面 我覺得啱啱好 唔會太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/154733_b533695d2dcc8c319514d86e82a82ca9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F154733_b533695d2dcc8c319514d86e82a82ca9.png&h=56bd11b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞翼方面 唔太識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個人嚟講唔太好呢一味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/160442_f21111ae080750d137cb6e9e3a8cf142.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F160442_f21111ae080750d137cb6e9e3a8cf142.png&h=c2f89f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影得有d差sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係專業打手<br />\n<br />\nOverall 唔錯 呢個價錢食到呢個質素 埋單都係108<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好過食KFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申中非打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef53f7d1e0c73bcc41b8800a04e1e2cc1113bb8b","tid":873143,"uid":126690,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7ea1736bddb726273529b971fa4c33e25e5290c","tid":873143,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"你地講左咁耐呢間野<br />\n即係係邊間熟食中心先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da792b5fc34